reviewText: Wont play on any DVD player
I liked that DVD came with a sticker sheet of all the badges from the episodes. My son watches this repeatedly, he loves Duggee !
I didn't realize this wasn't for my region when I bought it. Looking back its clearly noted. Completely my bad. If I can figure out how to jail break my DVD player, Ill be able to watch it
